@NODE Releases

	If you want me to include other libraries in O.F.L, you may send
	them to me along with the following files:

		- the library
		- the Include files, lib.i, fd.
		- its documentation
 
	I am particularly interested in the files related to the following
	libraries:

		- Arp.Library
		- XPK.Library.
		- 68040.Library
		- Decrunch.Library
		- Octaplayer.Library
		- Toolmanager.Library ......

	If you find mistakes in the libraries' functions, or bugs, please
	let me know of them so that I may solve the problem quickly.

